artists/PULP">Pulp</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-white">Foals</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/radiohead">Radiohead</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thom-yorke">Thom Yorke</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jONNY-GREENWOOD">Jonny Greenwood</a>等乐队都曾在那里出人意料地亮相。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bookies-odds-glastonbury-2024-secret-set-kasabian-kings-of-leon-pulp-3762814">格拉斯顿伯里 2024 年后：以下是博彩公司对谁将参加一场秘密比赛的赔率 - 对大型表演的投注暂停，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
